bitnami/postgresql-repmgr:latest\nnetworks:\n  - backend\nvolumes:\n  - ./pg-0:/bitnami/postgresql\n  - ./wiki.sql:/docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/wiki.sql\t\t# ONLY ON PG-0\nenvironment:\n  - POSTGRESQL_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n  - POSTGRESQL_PASSWORD=wikipassword\n  - POSTGRESQL_USERNAME=wikiuser\n  - POSTGRESQL_DATABASE=wikidb\n  - POSTGRESQL_NUM_SYNCHRONOUS_REPLICAS=1\n  - REPMGR_PRIMARY_HOST=pg-0\n  - REPMGR_NODE_NAME=pg-0\n  - REPMGR_NODE_NETWORK_NAME=pg-0\n  - REPMGR_PARTNER_NODES=pg-0,pg-1\n  - REPMGR_USERNAME=repmgr\n  - REPMGR_PASSWORD=repmgrpassword\n  - PASSWORD_AUTHENTICATION=md5\n```\n\nPGPool tarvitsee toimiakseen tietokantapalvelimille muuttujan PASSWORD_AUTHENTICATION=md5.\n\nHUOM! Muista vaihtaa salasanat ja kÃ¤yttÃ¤jÃ¤tunnukset ennen kuin siirryt tuotantokÃ¤yttÃ¶Ã¶n!\n\n## Docker Compose\n\ndocker-compose.yml kokonaisuudessaan [docker-compose.yml](/docker-compose.yml)\n```\nversion: '3.8'\n\nservices:\n  proxy:\n    image: nginxproxy/nginx-proxy:latest\n    ports:\n      - 80:80\n      - 443:443\n    volumes:\n      - /var/run/docker.sock:/tmp/docker.sock:ro\n    networks:\n      - frontend\n      - backend\n\n  wikijs:\n    image: requarks/wiki:2.5\n    networks:\n      - backend\n    deploy:\n      replicas: 2\n      restart_policy:\n        condition: on-failure\n    environment:\n      - VIRTUAL_HOST=wiki.colasloth.com\n#      IF WE WANT TO USE SSL INSTEAD, WE NEED TO COMMENT THE PREVIOUS LINE AND UNCOMMENT THE FOLLOWING LINES\n#      - VIRTUAL_PROTO=https\n#      - VIRTUAL_PORT=3443\n#      - SSL_ACTIVE=true\n#      - LETSENCRYPT_DOMAIN=wiki.colasloth.com\n#      - LETSENCRYPT_EMAIL=admin@colasloth.com\n#     ALSO COMMENT THE FOLLOWING LINE WHEN USING SSL.\n      - VIRTUAL_PORT=3000\n      - DB_TYPE=postgres\n      - DB_HOST=pgpool\n      - DB_PORT=5432\n      - DB_USER=wikiuser\n      - DB_PASS=wikipassword\n      - DB_NAME=wikidb\n      - HA_ACTIVE=true\n\n  pgpool:\n    image: bitnami/pgpool:latest\n    networks:\n      - backend\n    environment:\n      - PGPOOL_BACKEND_NODES=0:pg-0:5432,1:pg-1:5432\n      - PGPOOL_SR_CHECK_USER=repmgr\n      - PGPOOL_SR_CHECK_PASSWORD=repmgrpassword\n      - PGPOOL_ENABLE_LDAP=no\n      - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_USERNAME=postgres\n      - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n      - PGPOOL_ADMIN_USERNAME=admin\n      - PGPOOL_ADMIN_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n      - PGPOOL_ENABLE_LOAD_BALANCING=yes\n      - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_CUSTOM_USERS=wikiuser\n      - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_CUSTOM_PASSWORDS=wikipassword\n    healthcheck:\n      test: ["CMD", "/opt/bitnami/scripts/healthcheck.sh"]\n      interval: 10s\n      timeout: 5s\n      retries: 5\n\n  pg-0:\n    image: bitnami/postgresql-repmgr:latest\n    networks:\n      - backend\n    volumes:\n      - ./pg-0:/bitnami/postgresql\n      - ./wiki.sql:/docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/wiki.sql\n    environment:\n      - POSTGRESQL_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n      - POSTGRESQL_PASSWORD=wikipassword\n      - POSTGRESQL_USERNAME=wikiuser\n      - POSTGRESQL_DATABASE=wikidb\n      - POSTGRESQL_NUM_SYNCHRONOUS_REPLICAS=1\n      - REPMGR_PRIMARY_HOST=pg-0\n      - REPMGR_NODE_NAME=pg-0\n      - REPMGR_NODE_NETWORK_NAME=pg-0\n      - REPMGR_PARTNER_NODES=pg-0,pg-1\n      - REPMGR_USERNAME=repmgr\n      - REPMGR_PASSWORD=repmgrpassword\n      - PASSWORD_AUTHENTICATION=md5\n\n  pg-1:\n    image: bitnami/postgresql-repmgr:latest\n    networks:\n      - backend\n    volumes:\n      - ./pg-1:/bitnami/postgresql\n    environment:\n      - POSTGRESQL_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n      - POSTGRESQL_PASSWORD=wikipassword\n      - POSTGRESQL_USERNAME=wikiuser\n      - POSTGRESQL_DATABASE=wikidb\n      - POSTGRESQL_NUM_SYNCHRONOUS_REPLICAS=1\n      - REPMGR_PRIMARY_HOST=pg-0\n      - REPMGR_NODE_NAME=pg-1\n      - REPMGR_NODE_NETWORK_NAME=pg-1\n      - REPMGR_PARTNER_NODES=pg-0,pg-1\n      - REPMGR_USERNAME=repmgr\n      - REPMGR_PASSWORD=repmgrpassword\n      - PASSWORD_AUTHENTICATION=md5\n\nnetworks:\n  frontend:\n    driver: bridge\n  backend:\n    driver: bridge\n```\n\n	<h1 class="toc-header" id="docker-ympÃ¤ristÃ¶"><a href="#docker-ympÃ¤ristÃ¶" class="toc-anchor">Â¶</a> Docker-ympÃ¤ristÃ¶</h1>\n<p>HAMK Pilvipalvelut -kurssin docker-ympÃ¤ristÃ¶tyÃ¶<br>\nRisto Lievonen</p>\n<h2 class="toc-header" id="yleisrakenne"><a href="#yleisrakenne" class="toc-anchor">Â¶</a> Yleisrakenne</h2>\n<p>Rakennettu ympÃ¤ristÃ¶ sisÃ¤ltÃ¤Ã¤ kahdennetun Wiki.js palvelimen (josta tÃ¤tÃ¤ juuri luet), Nginx reverse proxyn,kahdennetun Postgres-tietokantapalvelimen ja niiden edessÃ¤ olevan tietokantaproxyn.</p>\n<p>UlospÃ¤in mainostetaan portit 80 ja 443, jotka ohjataan Nginx reverse proxylle. Reverse proxy ohjaa kyselyt eteenpÃ¤in Wiki.JS palveluun, porttiin 3000.</p>\n<p>Verkollisesti kontit on jaettu 2 eri verkkoon, frontend ja backend. Frontend-verkkoon pÃ¤Ã¤see ulkoa porteilla 80 ja 443 (vakiona) ja backend-verkkoon pÃ¤Ã¤see vain toisista konteista.</p>\n<div class="diagram"><svg viewBox="-0.5 -0.5 411 621" height="621px" width="411px" version="1.1" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><defs></defs><g><path stroke="none" fill="#dae8fc" d="M 0 90 L 410 90 L 410 620 L 0 620 L 0 90 Z"></path><path stroke="none" fill="none" d="M 5 95 L 5 615 L 5 615 L 405 615 L 405 95 L 5 95"></path><path stroke-dasharray="12 12" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke="#6c8ebf" fill="none" d="M 0 90 L 410 90 L 410 620 L 0 620 L 0 90 Z"></path><path stroke="none" fill="#f5f5f5" d="M 70 100 L 320 100 L 320 220 L 70 220 L 70 100 Z"></path><path stroke="none" fill="none" d="M 75 105 L 75 215 L 75 215 L 315 215 L 315 105 L 75 105"></path><path stroke-dasharray="3 3" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke="#666666" fill="none" d="M 70 100 L 320 100 L 320 220 L 70 220 L 70 100 Z"></path><path stroke="none" fill="#f8cecc" d="M 80 170 L 380 170 L 380 600 L 80 600 L 80 170 Z"></path><path stroke="none" fill="none" d="M 85 175 L 85 595 L 85 595 L 375 595 L 375 175 L 85 175"></path><path stroke-dasharray="3 3" stroke-miterlimit="10" str