\n  - backend\ndeploy:\n  replicas: 2\n  restart_policy:\n    condition: on-failure\nenvironment:\n  - VIRTUAL_HOST=wiki.colasloth.com\n#  IF WE WANT TO USE SSL INSTEAD, WE NEED TO COMMENT THE PREVIOUS LINE AND UNCOMMENT THE FOLLOWING LINES\n#  - VIRTUAL_PROTO=https\n#  - VIRTUAL_PORT=3443\n#  - SSL_ACTIVE=true\n#  - LETSENCRYPT_DOMAIN=wiki.colasloth.com\n#  - LETSENCRYPT_EMAIL=admin@colasloth.com\n#  ALSO COMMENT THE FOLLOWING LINE WHEN USING SSL.\n  - VIRTUAL_PORT=3000\n  - DB_TYPE=postgres\n  - DB_HOST=pgpool\n  - DB_PORT=5432\n  - DB_USER=wikiuser\n  - DB_PASS=wikipassword\n  - DB_NAME=wikidb\n  - HA_ACTIVE=true\n</code></pre>\n<h4 class="toc-header" id="yleiset-asetukset"><a href="#yleiset-asetukset" class="toc-anchor">Â¶</a> Yleiset asetukset</h4>\n<p>Kontti on kahdennettu, jolloin kÃ¤ynnissÃ¤ on aina 2 wiki konttia. Replikoiden mÃ¤Ã¤rÃ¤Ã¤ voi muuttaa docker-compose.yml tiedostosta.</p>\n<p>Kahdennetussa ympÃ¤ristÃ¶ssÃ¤ pitÃ¤Ã¤ aina ympÃ¤ristÃ¶muuttuja HA_ACTIVE olla joko <code>true</code> tai <code>1</code>.</p>\n<pre v-pre="true" class="prismjs line-numbers"><code class="language-">deploy:\n  replicas: 2\nenvironment:\n  - HA_ACTIVE=true\n</code></pre>\n<h4 class="toc-header" id="proxyasetukset"><a href="#proxyasetukset" class="toc-anchor">Â¶</a> Proxyasetukset</h4>\n<p>Kontin proxyasetukset tehdÃ¤Ã¤n ympÃ¤ristÃ¶muuttujilla. Jos halutaan kÃ¤yttÃ¤Ã¤ HTTPS-protokollaa HTTP:n sijaan, pitÃ¤Ã¤ asetuksia muokata sen mukaan.</p>\n<pre v-pre="true" class="prismjs line-numbers"><code class="language-">environment:\n  - VIRTUAL_HOST=wiki.colasloth.com\n#  IF WE WANT TO USE SSL INSTEAD, WE NEED TO COMMENT THE PREVIOUS LINE AND UNCOMMENT THE FOLLOWING LINES\n#  - VIRTUAL_PROTO=https\n#  - VIRTUAL_PORT=3443\n#  - SSL_ACTIVE=true\n#  - LETSENCRYPT_DOMAIN=wiki.colasloth.com\n#  - LETSENCRYPT_EMAIL=admin@colasloth.com\n#  ALSO COMMENT THE FOLLOWING LINE WHEN USING SSL.\n  - VIRTUAL_PORT=3000\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ottamalla SSL-asetukset kÃ¤yttÃ¶Ã¶n, luodaan palvelulle SSL-varmenne automaattisesti LetsEncrypt palvelulla. TÃ¤llÃ¶in sivuston pitÃ¤Ã¤ olla saavutettavissa internetistÃ¤.</p>\n<h4 class="toc-header" id="tietokanta-asetukset"><a href="#tietokanta-asetukset" class="toc-anchor">Â¶</a> Tietokanta-asetukset</h4>\n<p>Palvelun tietokantana toimii PostgreSQL. Tietokannan voi rakentaa yhdelle kontille, mutta tÃ¤ssÃ¤ tapauksessa tietokanta on replikoitu ja sille on rakennettu 2 konttia. pg-0 ja pg-1 pitÃ¤vÃ¤t sisÃ¤llÃ¤Ã¤n varsinaisen tietokannan, ja pgpool toimii palvelulle vÃ¤ylÃ¤nÃ¤ tietokantaan.</p>\n<p>Palvelun kyselyt ohjataan siis pgpool kontille, joka puolestaan valvoo replikoitujen tietokantojen tilaa ja ohjaa kyselyt aktiiviselle tietokannalle.</p>\n<pre v-pre="true" class="prismjs line-numbers"><code class="language-">environment:\n  - DB_TYPE=postgres\n  - DB_HOST=pgpool\n  - DB_PORT=5432\n  - DB_USER=wikiuser\n  - DB_PASS=wikipassword\n  - DB_NAME=wikidb\n  - HA_ACTIVE=true\n</code></pre>\n<p>Muista vaihtaa kÃ¤yttÃ¤jÃ¤tunnukset ja salasanat ennen tuotantokÃ¤yttÃ¶Ã¤!</p>\n<h3 class="toc-header" id="pgpool"><a href="#pgpool" class="toc-anchor">Â¶</a> PGPool</h3>\n<p>PGPool on tietokantojen replikointia valvova tyÃ¶kalu, joka toimii asiakassovelluksen (tÃ¤ssÃ¤ tapauksessa wiki) ja tietokannan vÃ¤lissÃ¤.</p>\n<p>PGPoolin docker-imagen ohjeet lÃ¶ytyvÃ¤t <a class="is-external-link" href="https://hub.docker.com/r/bitnami/pgpool">Docker hubista</a>.</p>\n<p>Kontin asetukset</p>\n<pre v-pre="true" class="prismjs line-numbers"><code class="language-">image: bitnami/pgpool:latest\nnetworks:\n  - backend\nenvironment:\n  - PGPOOL_BACKEND_NODES=0:pg-0:5432,1:pg-1:5432\n  - PGPOOL_SR_CHECK_USER=repmgr\n  - PGPOOL_SR_CHECK_PASSWORD=repmgrpassword\n  - PGPOOL_ENABLE_LDAP=no\n  - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_USERNAME=postgres\n  - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n  - PGPOOL_ADMIN_USERNAME=admin\n  - PGPOOL_ADMIN_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n  - PGPOOL_ENABLE_LOAD_BALANCING=yes\n  - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_CUSTOM_USERS=wikiuser\n  - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_CUSTOM_PASSWORDS=wikipassword\nhealthcheck:\n  test: ["CMD", "/opt/bitnami/scripts/healthcheck.sh"]\n  interval: 10s\n  timeout: 5s\n  retries: 5\n</code></pre>\n<p>Kontille mÃ¤Ã¤ritellÃ¤Ã¤n PGPOOL_BACKEND_NODES muuttujalla kaikki sen valvonnassa olevat tietokannat. Jos niistÃ¤ jokin lakkaa vastaamasta, siirrytÃ¤Ã¤n autommaattisesti toiseen.</p>\n<p>HUOM! Muista vaihtaa salasanat ja kÃ¤yttÃ¤jÃ¤tunnukset ennen kuin siirryt tuotantokÃ¤yttÃ¶Ã¶n!</p>\n<h3 class="toc-header" id="pg-0-ja-pg-1"><a href="#pg-0-ja-pg-1" class="toc-anchor">Â¶</a> PG-0 ja PG-1</h3>\n<p>PG-0 ja PG-1 ovat periaatteessa tavallisia PostgreSQL-palvelimia, mutta niihin on lisÃ¤tty valmiiksi replikointi.</p>\n<p>YmpÃ¤ristÃ¶muuttujissa mÃ¤Ã¤ritetÃ¤Ã¤n ensisijainen tietokantapalvelin ja kaikki replikoinnissa mukana olevat palvelimet.</p>\n<p>Konttiin on sidottu kaksi kansiota, pg-0 (pg-1 toisessa palvelimessa) johon tietokannan data tallennetaan ja wiki.sql (vain pg-0, ei muille palvelimille), jolla wikipalvelun data tuodaan tietokantaan.</p>\n<pre v-pre="true" class="prismjs line-numbers"><code class="language-">image: bitnami/postgresql-repmgr:latest\nnetworks:\n  - backend\nvolumes:\n  - ./pg-0:/bitnami/postgresql\n  - ./wiki.sql:/docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/wiki.sql\t\t# ONLY ON PG-0\nenvironment:\n  - POSTGRESQL_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n  - POSTGRESQL_PASSWORD=wikipassword\n  - POSTGRESQL_USERNAME=wikiuser\n  - POSTGRESQL_DATABASE=wikidb\n  - POSTGRESQL_NUM_SYNCHRONOUS_REPLICAS=1\n  - REPMGR_PRIMARY_HOST=pg-0\n  - REPMGR_NODE_NAME=pg-0\n  - REPMGR_NODE_NETWORK_NAME=pg-0\n  - REPMGR_PARTNER_NODES=pg-0,pg-1\n  - REPMGR_USERNAME=repmgr\n  - REPMGR_PASSWORD=repmgrpassword\n  - PASSWORD_AUTHENTICATION=md5\n</code></pre>\n<p>PGPool tarvitsee toimiakseen tietokantapalvelimille muuttujan PASSWORD_AUTHENTICATION=md5.</p>\n<p>HUOM! Muista vaihtaa salasanat ja kÃ¤yttÃ¤jÃ¤tunnukset ennen kuin siirryt tuotantokÃ¤yttÃ¶Ã¶n!</p>\n<h2 class="toc-header" id="docker-compose"><a href="#docker-compose" class="toc-anchor">Â¶</a> Docker Compose</h2>\n<p>docker-compose.yml kokonaisuudessaan <a class="is-asset-link" href="/docker-compose.yml">docker-compose.yml</a></p>\n<pre v-pre="true" class="prismjs line-numbers"><code class="language-">version: '3.8'\n\nservices:\n  proxy:\n    image: nginxproxy/nginx-proxy:latest\n    ports:\n      - 80:80\n      - 443:443\n    volumes:\n      - /var/run/docker.sock:/tmp/docker.sock:ro\n    networks:\n      - frontend\n      - backend\n\n  wikijs:\n    image: requarks/wiki:2.5\n    networks:\n      - backend\n    deploy:\n      replicas: 2\n      restart_policy:\n        condition: on-failure\n    environment:\n      - VIRTUAL_HOST=wiki.colasloth.com\n#      IF WE WANT TO USE SSL INSTEAD, WE NEED TO COMMENT THE PREVIOUS LINE AND UNCOMMENT THE FOLLOWING LINES\n#      - VIRTUAL_PROTO=https\n#      - VIRTUAL_PORT=3443\n#      - SSL_ACTIVE=true\n#      - LETSENCRYPT_DOMAIN=wiki.colasloth.com\n#      - LETSENCRYPT_EMAIL=admin@colasloth.com\n#     ALSO COMMENT THE FOLLOWING LINE WHEN USING SSL.\n      - VIRTUAL_PORT=3000\n      - DB_TYPE=postgres\n      - DB_HOST=pgpool\n      - DB_PORT=5432\n      - DB_USER=wikiuser\n      - DB_PASS=wikipassword\n      - DB_NAME=wikidb\n      - HA_ACTIVE=true\n\n  pgpool:\n    image: bitnami/pgpool:latest\n    networks:\n      - backend\n    environment:\n      - PGPOOL_BACKEND_NODES=0:pg-0:5432,1:pg-1:5432\n      - PGPOOL_SR_CHECK_USER=repmgr\n      - PGPOOL_SR_CHECK_PASSWORD=repmgrpassword\n      - PGPOOL_ENABLE_LDAP=no\n      - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_USERNAME=postgres\n      - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n      - PGPOOL_ADMIN_USERNAME=admin\n      - PGPOOL_ADMIN_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n      - PGPOOL_ENABLE_LOAD_BALANCING=yes\n      - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_CUSTOM_USERS=wikiuser\n      - PGPOOL_POSTGRES_CUSTOM_PASSWORDS=wikipassword\n    healthcheck:\n      test: ["CMD", "/opt/bitnami/scripts/healthcheck.sh"]\n      interval: 10s\n      timeout: 5s\n      retries: 5\n\n  pg-0:\n    image: bitnami/postgresql-repmgr:latest\n    networks:\n      - backend\n    volumes:\n      - ./pg-0:/bitnami/postgresql\n      - ./wiki.sql:/docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/wiki.sql\n    environment:\n      - POSTGRESQL_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n      - POSTGRESQL_PASSWORD=wikipassword\n      - POSTGRESQL_USERNAME=wikiuser\n      - POSTGRESQL_DATABASE=wikidb\n      - POSTGRESQL_NUM_SYNCHRONOUS_REPLICAS=1\n      - REPMGR_PRIMARY_HOST=pg-0\n      - REPMGR_NODE_NAME=pg-0\n      - REPMGR_NODE_NETWORK_NAME=pg-0\n      - REPMGR_PARTNER_NODES=pg-0,pg-1\n      - REPMGR_USERNAME=repmgr\n      - REPMGR_PASSWORD=repmgrpassword\n      - PASSWORD_AUTHENTICATION=md5\n\n  pg-1:\n    image: bitnami/postgresql-repmgr:latest\n    networks:\n      - backend\n    volumes:\n      - ./pg-1:/bitnami/postgresql\n    environment:\n      - POSTGRESQL_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=adminpassword\n      - POSTGRESQL_PASSWORD=wikipassword\n      - POSTGRESQL_USERNAME=wikiuser\n      - POSTGRESQL_DATABASE=wikidb\n      - POSTGRESQL_NUM_SYNCHRONOUS_REPLICAS=1\n      - REPMGR_PRIMARY_HOST=pg-0\n      - REPMGR_NODE_NAME=pg-1\n      - REPMGR_NODE_NETWORK_NAME=pg-1\n      - REPMGR_PARTNER_NODES=pg-0,pg-1\n      - REPMGR_USERNAME=repmgr\n      - REPMGR_PASSWORD=repmgrpassword\n      - PASSWORD_AUTHENTICATION=md5\n\nnetworks:\n  frontend:\n    driver: bridge\n  backend:\n    driver: bridge\n</code></pre>\n	[{"title":"Docker-ympÃ¤ristÃ¶","anchor":"#docker-ympÃ¤ristÃ¶","children":[{"title":"Yleisrakenne","anchor":"#yleisrakenne","children":[]},{"title":"Kontit","anchor":"#kontit","children":[{"title":"Proxy","anchor":"#proxy","children":[]},{"title":"Wiki","anchor":"#wiki","children":[{"title":"Yleiset asetukset","anchor":"#yleiset-asetukset","children":[]},{"title":"Proxyasetukset","anchor":"#proxyasetukset","children":[]},{"title":"Tietokanta-asetukset","anchor":"#tietokanta-asetukset","children":[]}]},{"title":"PGPool","anchor":"#pgpool","children":[]},{"title":"PG-0 ja PG-1","anchor":"#pg-0-ja-pg-1","children":[]}]},{"title":"Docker Compose","ancho